<Content>Good hotel in Florence, very nice staff The folks at Bodoni were very nice and helpful; they are multilingual and easy to get along with. The room was nice for a discount hotel. Bed was typical of Europe. It was fairly convenient from the train station. It was quiet and the bathroom was nice. Overall, one of the nicer places we stayed in Europe. 
